'''Arrg''' is a [[quest]] monster that must be defeated during [[Troll Romance]].

Arrg is the second strongest mountain [[troll]], surpassed only by [[Kob]] from the [[Monkey Madness II]] quest. He uses both [[melee]] and [[ranged]]. He teleports the player to the [[Troll arena]] to fight.

Arrg can only be fought during the quest, and afterwards he can be fought in the [[Nightmare Zone]].

==Strategy==
{{Main|Troll Romance#Fighting Arrg}}
[[File:Troll Romance - Arrg safespot.png|thumb|left|250px|The safespot for fighting Arrg.]]
Arrg can be safespotted during the arena fight, in a similar fashion to [[Dad]], by trapping him behind the mountain wall to the west and standing by the fence. This negates the need to use [[Prayer|prayers]] and simply requires the player to tank the initial hits taken while moving to the safespot, as you start in the centre of the arena.

Players can use a combination of [[protect from melee]] and [[protect from Missiles|ranged]], and negate damage by switching prayers as he switches attacks. This can be tricky, however, due to his 4-tick attack speed, his ability to penetrate prayers, and the lack of warning prior to him switching attacks.

