==Trivia==
* Unlike most trolls, Arrg drops regular [[bones]] instead of [[big bones]] outside of the [[Nightmare Zone]].
* Most trolls are named after the first thing they eat; if the first thing eaten is unknown, they're named after the sound the thing they ate made, which in this case was "arrg". This is revealed in a [[Postbag from the Hedge]] from November 2007, {{RSL|Transcript:The trouble with trolls|The trouble with trolls}}.

